School Kits Limited commenced business in 2000 as a professional school outfitting firm and the pioneer one-stop shop for a wide range of requirements for students from pre-school age through the secondary (High) school age. Since its inception, it has experienced significant growth to becoming a credible brand within the school supplies industry in Nigeria. Our competence and credibility can be attested to by many satisfied clients from start-ups schools to well-established institutions as listed in our portfolio. The company is steered by a sound and innovative management team along with over 200 members spread across 9 business locations in Lagos, Ibadan, Abuja, Maiduguri and Damaturu. The brand has grown significantly over the years and diversified its portfolio into four strategic business units namely Retail, Wholesale/ Distribution, Garment Production and Humanitarian Aid Supplies evolving in the rebranding of the company name from School Kits limited to SKLD integrated Services Limited in 2020 in the 20th year of its operations. We are recruiting to fill the position below: Location: LagosEmployment Type: Full-time Duties and Responsibilities Key Requirements Application Closing Date30th December, 2020. The post Graphic Design Executive at SKLD Integrated Services Limited appeared first on Jobs in Nigeria â€“ http://jobsinnigeria.careers. Get all the Latest news, Breaking headlines,Sport, Education, Finance, Gists, Jobs, Music/Video, Technology and Top stories in real time in Nigeria and around the world.